                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>5 William St</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Room No 4</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>Sept 16. 1863</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Reverend Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I beg<lb/> leave to inform you that I have<lb/> just received per\n                Steamer from<lb/>\n                <placeName>Jamaica</placeName> a lot of Sulabs<add>?</add> &amp;<lb/> Citrons, and I\n                shall feel obliged<lb/> by your informing me per return<lb/> of mail if I can send\n                you a<lb/>\n                <sic>a</sic> small quantity of them and<lb/> request the favor of your\n                disposing<lb/> of same. I have reason<lb/> to believe that they are better<lb/> than\n                those I received last year<lb/> as they have been selected by</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3hm5351q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
