                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>a friend with great care.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Should you be willing to<lb/> receive the Sulabs<add>?</add> &amp;\n                Citrons please<lb/> inform what quantity I must<lb/> trouble you with.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Wishing you a happy<lb/> New Year, and a pleasant<lb/> fast.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">I am Reverend Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">yours very respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Solomon Lazarus</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
